      "id": 1,
      "text": "Glen Aubrey began as Councilman Settlement, named for early farmer Philip Councilman who arrived in 1793 and cleared the land.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4,
        17,
        19
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
